html(data-theme=" ")
  include partials/_head.pug
  body.bg-secondary(class="max-w-[2200px]").m-auto
    include partials/_nav.pug
    section.m-4.text-primary
        h1.text-6xl.text-center.my-8 Welcome to your dashboard!
        if studentList.length > 0
          section.bg-info.card
            section.grid.gap-8.p-4.px-8(class='md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3')
              for student in studentList
                div.card.relative.p-6.border-secondary.shadow-lg.bg-base-100
                  div.top-4.right-4.absolute.delete__button.cursor-pointer(id=student.ID) 
                    i.fa-regular.fa-trash-can.text-accent
                  a(href="/student/searchStudentPage?ID="+student.ID class="text-center ") 
                    span.text-3xl.text-accent.card-title.justify-center=student.firstName.toUpperCase() + ' ' + student.lastName.toUpperCase()
                  div.divider.mt-0.mb-0(class='before:bg-secondary after:bg-secondary')
                  table.table-auto.text-center.text-md.text-accent
                    tbody
                      tr
                        td Student ID
                        td= student.ID
                      tr 
                        td Exceptionality
                        td= student.primaryExceptionality
                      tr
                        td Case Manager
                        td=  student.caseManager.firstName[0]+student.caseManager.lastName
                      tr
                        td IEP Due Date
                        if student.IEPDueDate
                          td= student.IEPDueDate.toDateString().split(' ').splice(1, 4).join(' ')
                        else 
                          td IEP
        else 
          section.py-8.text-lg(class='md:text-xl lg:text-2xl xl:text-3xl lg:px-12')
            p Welcome to ESE-At-A-Glance! This application is for teachers of ESE students and serves as a one-stop shop to see your students' IEP goal history and accommodations. This message will show until you add a student (using the "Add") button above. You may also use the "Search" button to search for other students. Student number "123" is already set up to display what the information should look like. If you have any questions please #[a(href="mailto:bschefstad@gmail.com") email me] or #[a.underline(href="https://github.com/Brandon-Schefstad/ESEAtAGlance/issues") submit an issue on GitHub.] Thank you! 
          section.grid(class='lg:px-12')
            section.mb-8
              p.text-xl(class='md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl pb-6') If you are unfamiliar with IEP's, FAPE, or IDEA, please watch this short video: 
              iframe( src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7qkNsR6Cgsk" title="What Are IEPs? IEP, IDEA, and Special Education Services Explained" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen class='w-full h-[450px] md:h-[550px] lg:h-[650px] xl:h-[750px]') 
            section
              p.text-xl(class='md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl pb-6') For more explanations about IEP goals, please watch: 
              iframe( src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q4m0rnrP2kA" title="Federally Mandated Elements / IEP: Measurable Goals" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen class='w-full h-[450px] md:h-[550px] lg:h-[650px] xl:h-[750px]')
  include partials/_footer.pug
  //- test